hoping from flower to flower \'til she
spotted a very cute and pudgy Bunny.

so that his new friend would not say goodbye.

\\n\\n\\n\\n

looking for some squishy,mushy honey
hoping from flower to flower \'til she
spotted a very cute and pudgy Bunny.

\\n\\n\\n\\n

Shining in the sun his little round nose
looked and smelled such a lot like honey
that she then lit upon his soft sweet snout
but it was furry and felt very funny.

\\n\\n\\n\\n

Wondering who this strange creature might be
Bunny stared hard with his bright blue eye
trying not to move or let out a sneeze
so that his new friend would not say goodbye.

\\n\\n\\n\\n

But his soft snout was a spout so gentle
that her whiskey whiskers did really tickle
and should she ever attempt to bite him
then he\'d really be in a right pickle.

\\n\\n\\n\\n
